value.title: GOP letter to Biden flags Afghan evacuees' 'rushed and incomplete' vetting

value.title: Fact check: Image of Kamala Harris and Doug Emhoff altered to show Jeffrey Epstein

value.title: Biden administration wants solar power to increase tenfold in 15 years

value.excerpt: The former president and his team, sensing a political opportunity, have issued more than 50 statements about Afghanistan, and his PAC has raised millions with repeated fundraising pitches on the topic.
